# THE decode profile for arena_modes.proto -- must stay in lockstep with
# tests/arena_modes_profile.hpp (the in-test spelling of the same selection): the regen script
# generates the goldens through THIS file, the tests re-generate them through the header, and the
# golden comparison fails if the two ever diverge.
name lean

drop fm.Holder.debug
drop fm.Holder.extra
drop fm.Holder.old_ids

# The type entry covers blob, blobs, and req_blob -- and silently skips the by_name map.
raw fm.Blob
raw fm.Holder.grp
